ommandons de v&#233;rifier les horaires de vos trains.<\/p>","shortMessage":"Trafic perturbé","disruption_id":"2152ca76-6559-452a-a386-6b9f6d32a9f3"},{"id":"ba671580-e296-4f12-9b3f-01ea9c6de73f","applicationPeriods":[{"begin":"20260429T130640","end":"20260429T143000"}],"lastUpdate":"20260429T133545","cause":"PERTURBATION","severity":"PERTURBEE","title":"Ligne J : fortes perturbations","message":"<p>Le trafic est fortement perturb&#233; entre Paris Saint-Lazare et Gisors et entre Paris Saint-Lazare et Mantes-la-Jolie via Conflans Ste-H. dans les 2 sens.<br><br>Pour plus d'informations sur cette perturbation, consultez le <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/LIGNEJ_SNCF\">fil X de la ligne J<\/a>.<br><br>Motif : individus sur les voies (entre Cormeilles-en-Parisis et la Frette-Montigny).<\/p>","shortMessage":"Trafic fortement perturbé","impactedSections":[{"lineId":"line:IDFM:C01739","from":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:71370","name":"Gare Saint-Lazare (Paris)"},"to":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:65931","name":"Mantes-la-Jolie (Mantes-la-Jolie)"}},{"lineId":"line:IDFM:C01739","from":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:71370","name":"Gare Saint-Lazare (Paris)"},"to":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:74348","name":"Gisors (Gisors)"}},{"lineId":"line:IDFM:C01739","from":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:74348","name":"Gisors (Gisors)"},"to":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:71370","name":"Gare Saint-Lazare (Paris)"}},{"lineId":"line:IDFM:C01739","from":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:65931","name":"Mantes-la-Jolie (Mantes-la-Jolie)"},"to":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:71370","name":"Gare Saint-Lazare (Paris)"}}],"disruption_id":"9a513676-4b73-4d80-9b4c-569412c99c6c"},{"id":"5850584b-d9c7-4289-884a-1cdce582f0e2","applicationPeriods":[{"begin":"20260419T092500","end":"20260501T235900"}],"lastUpdate":"20260425T173016","cause":"PERTURBATION","severity":"PERTURBEE","title":"Tramway  T11 - Mouvement social : Trafi